        <abstract>
            The dataset is a compilation of nature monitoring data collected by persons related to Amphi Consult or Biomedia during multiple different consulting projects. The dataset covers approximately 47.300 registrations of Animalia, Fungi, Plantae, and Protozoa from Denmark made from 1969 until 2016.
        </abstract>
